6. DATA WE COLLECT
6.1 While using Our Service, We may ask Users to provide Us with certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify Users. Personally identifiable information may include, but is not limited to:
Email address
First name and last name
Public profile picture of Email, Facebook and Gmail accounts, depending on the account choice of signup process
This collection of information is only available when User creates an account on Muslim Assistant app through third-party services like Email signup, Facebook signup, Google Signup options.
User agrees that, by creating an account, consent is given to Muslim Assistant app to send emails for, including but not limited to, new account creation, password reset or payment failure occasions.
Muslim Assistant keeps activity progress of the User, with an associated account that, In any case of data loss or inability to access an account or log in, Muslim Assistant app doesn’t have a legal obligation to restore the data back or provide the service to the User.
If the Users accidentally create additional accounts on Muslim Assistant app, which may consist of choices of multiple Google, Facebook or Email accounts, Users must be aware that all accounts are separate and can not be tied or combined unless they have been created with the same email address. Users could demand account deletion of accidentally created accounts by contacting
help@muslimassistant.com
email address.
6.2 DELETION OF INFORMATION
Retention of collected data subjects to the Third Party companies limits, which are listed at 2.2. Of Muslim Assistant or any other apps of Muslim Assistant
Muslim Assistant App does not save personal data which are listed at 2.2, in It's server unless User creates an account as declared on 6.1.
If User creates an account and prefers their account to be deleted, there are a few steps to complete the deletion:
User must go to settings, tap my profile screen and  tap to “delete account” at the footer. Then the account information from the Muslim Assistant app’s Database will be deleted automatically. User will see “Account is successfully deleted” message after deletion is complete.
It will take approximately 48 hours to apply the changes on the app. User can no longer login unless creating a new account.
User needs to delete Social Login (Facebook or Google Login) app activities themself. Steps are mentioned below.
User’s Account Information Deletion for Facebook Login
If User wants to delete their activities on Muslim Assistant of a Facebook account, Users have the choice to remove their information and delete their account by following these steps:
Go to Facebook Account’s Setting & Privacy. Tap “Settings”
Look for “Apps and Websites” and you will see all of the apps and websites you linked with your Facebook.
Search and tap “Muslim Assistant” in the search bar.
Tap “Remove”.
App activities are successfully removed from Muslim Assistant app.
If Muslim Assistant app could not be found at the search result mentioned on step 3,  which is "Apps and Websites" search, that means the Muslim Assistant app activities are not stored in a Facebook account.
User’s Account Information Deletion for Google Login
If User wants to delete their activities on Muslim Assistant of a Google account, Users have the choice to remove their information and delete their account by following these steps:
Go to Google Account settings
Under “Services on this device” title, go to “Settings for Google Apps”
Tap Connected Apps
Choose Muslim Assistant App among the list
Tap “Disconnect”
App activities are successfully removed from Muslim Assistant app.
If Muslim Assistant app could not be found at the search result mentioned on step 4,  which is "Choose Muslim Assistant App among the list" search, that means the Muslim Assistant app activities are not stored in a Google account.
Besides Facebook and Google, Users could request to delete the account information of their email account that have been created on Muslim Assistant App, by contacting help@muslimassistant.com  email address.
Muslim Assistant app is also available to use without an account creation where Muslim Assistant app has the reserve the right to make changes of the use or purpose of  the accounts.
Important:
Deletion of account does not end an existing Subscription or Lifetime purchase. For subscription cancellation; App Store’s, Google Play Store’s or  Huawei Mobile Services’ cancellation policies apply.
For Apple auto-renewable subscription cancellation:
https://apps.apple.com/account/subscriptions
For Google Play auto-renewable  subscription cancellation:
https://play.google.com/store/account/subscriptions
